                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>e) maxuu yahay natiijada baaritaan caafimaad ee ka soo baxay iyo darajada ama nooca dhaawaca?</label>
                    <label>Tusaale: dhaawac fudud *, dhaawac culus ** ama dhaawac aad u culus ***</label>
                    <textarea class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="definitions">
                    <h4>*dhaawac fudud:</h4>
                    <p>dhaawac fudud baa loo qaadanayaa hadii nabarku uu keeno bukaan ku saabsan xagga jirka</p>

                    <h4>**dhaawac culus:</h4>
                    <p>dhaawac culus baa loo qaadanayaa</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>[b] haddii uu nabarku keenayo bukaan halis gelinayo nafta qofka wax la yeelay ama awoodii qofka u keenay in uu qabsan waayo hawsha caadiga ah muddo ka kooban 40 maalmood</li>
                        <li>[t] haddii uu nabarku itaal darro joogto ah u keenayo dareen (senso) ama xubin []</li>
                        <li>[i] haddii la rido ilig caafiaad qaba</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4>***dhaawac aad u culus:</h4>
                    <p>dhaawac aad u culus baa loo qaadanayaa haddii nabarku uu keenayo:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>[b] bukaan la hubo ama laga yaabo inaan la daaweyn Karin</li>
                        <li>[t] dareen luma (la perdita di un senso)</li>
